  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TutorialStep
  id: conversation02
  text: "CHARM:\nIn the same way Luke\u2019s Confidence level affects how HE talks
    to Daisy, Daisy\u2019s Charm level affects how SHE responds to Luke.\n\nDaisy\u2019s
    responses can further impact Luke\u2019s Confidence \u2013 positively or negatively..
    \n\nCharm is only indicated by Daisy\u2019s body language and responses to Luke,
    so pay attention! \n\nIf Daisy\u2019s Charm hits zero, the loop resets."
  boxSize: {x: 600, y: 300}
  boxAnchoredPosition: {x: 0, y: 0}
  dismissMode: 0
  showBackdrop: 1
